3.0.15.description: IBM Order management Software Enterprise Edition v10 provides cross-channel order orchestration capabilities to enable intelligent brokering of orders across many disparate systems. It also provides a global view of inventory across the supply chain and enables business users to make changes to order process. For additional details regarding install parameters check [Installing Sterling Order Management Software using Certified Container](https://www.ibm.com/docs/en/order-management-sw/10.0?topic=installing-sterling-order-management-software-using-certified-container). By installing this product you accept the license terms: [Sterling OMS License Agreement](http://ibm.biz/oms-license) and [Call Center and Store License Agreement](http://ibm.biz/oms-apps-license).
